{
  "version": "2025-10-31T11:05:00-05:00",
  "description": "CENTRAL: daily/weekly/monthly/seasonal + sabbath-prep routines for Suka Smart Assistant. Feeds Cleaning Session Planner, Home dashboard, ImportService, and automation/runtime.js. User-owned favorites and schedules supported. Reverse generation enabled so meal, garden, animal/butchery, and storehouse events can request appropriate cleaning routines.",
  "meta": {
